description:
This DAO is a proposition to unite the entire NFT space into coming together in the pursuit of getting one of the few black checks that will ever be created. 

1 Check, every hour until we get the black check. All the funds will be destined to accumulate checks. 

Jack Butcher has been adding value to his community in massive ways, for years now. He has made a name for himself by creating a very unique type of art that has inspired many others to start a career in the design space. It was only a matter of time until one of his creations would have the impact that Checks are having in the community right now. An Open Edition that the whole NFT space has been talking about for weeks now. 

For those that have been part of Jack's community, this comes as no surprise since he has been sharing value day in and day out. From philosophical tweets to unique pieces of art, his community is one of the most active communities someone can be a part of. His giving mentality has inspired the creators of this DAO to start something that will bring amazing people together, like-minded humans that can create an impact in the world through checks. The possibilities are endless once we achieve our goal. 

This is an opportunity to allow people to wear a PFP that represents the Checks movement. The art has been inspired by Jack's works and pieces of art, and if you feel called to it, we would love to have you in the community.
